{"tid":2026774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"35歲戴夢夢跟54歲太極Ricky一度分手：我冇後悔過","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:50:01.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"566849efda66e94c70af81ac6bd2142c02a3dd3a","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"現年35歲的戴夢夢，15年被揭跟人夫，太極鼓手Ricky深夜當街啜爆，大醉的她更激動得除裙。原來，當時51歲的Ricky仍未離婚，跟任職銀行高層的太太ANNE育有一子，被指小三的戴夢夢自然受千夫所指。其後，Ricky理清三角關係，跟太太分開，並正式和戴夢夢出席公開活動，大方承認關係。不過，拍拖年多，17年中，兩人又告分手。戴夢夢被拍到跟一名男士行街。"},{"pid":"1b825f2df47363b46e56e6848ba1ddd9341393c0","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"「我同Ricky步伐不一致，雖然努力過，不過都係唔得。但大家都依然係好朋友，經常有聯絡，或者轉一種方式相處會更好。」戴夢夢在分手後，曾經向傳媒透露，她未有後悔愛過Ricky，兩人也不是為了激情才開始一段關係，因大家都是成年人。<br />\n<br />\n而比戴夢夢大19年的Ricky，更加感謝她付出：「她是個好女仔，希望佢搵到一個好男人，有幸褔生活。」"},{"pid":"7b284d9c285675d71a9aef8de8f117dfcd707c07","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"事實，戴夢夢跟Ricky拍拖，也會間中跟他的兒子三人行。原來，Ricky兒子患有過度活躍症，身形長得跟爸爸一樣高大的他，大部份時間都要有工人姐姐陪同才外出，戴夢夢未有抗拒之餘，更會幫忙照顧，減輕Ricky負擔。故Ricky對女友付出，盡在不言中。"},{"pid":"8302f319f23c0dce3e35f57b6fe919824097ccd4","tid":2026774,"uid":233268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"78208e7f5f4aecc2ab6eb72838dd96114fc5f9b2","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200520/1536pix/1589957813_2be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200520%2F1536pix%2F1589957813_2be2.jpg&h=c16cf979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n95年，當年只有6歲的她跟甄子丹在電視劇《精武門》有對手戲。"},{"pid":"a578ee6da63d69011a33d8156fe5935317af7443","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"結緍計劃告吹<br />\n<br />\n分手後數個月，兩人又再被發現復合。<br />\n<br />\n這一天，他們出動去食海鮮餐，戴夢夢對Ricky兒子十分照顧，同枱吃飯，Ricky行開行埋，她便會坐近身邊跟他傾偈。有時又會用手機玩拍照，令經常要離枱的Ricky兒子乖乖坐定，十分有耐性。難怪Ricky在太極演唱會中，曾公開：「佢好好，好照顧我，對我不離不棄。」"},{"pid":"9912bc5705f622cba7b3c48e38404b4429ac8ad3","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"戴夢夢六歲入行，參加過不少童星比賽，因而有機會拍過不少當年亞視的大製作，其中有《飄零燕》和《再見豔陽天》，十多歲時，她又簽約唱片公司出碟，不過演藝事業一般。緋聞也寥寥可數，跟相士陳定幫拍過拖，一度談婚論嫁，最終因被發現她有第三者而分開，又有說傅穎才是第三者。到簽約大明娛樂後數年，她索性轉戰幕後，協力老闆林建明打理娛樂部門，參與不少演唱會、舞台劇和唱片製作。"},{"pid":"56ec071f4fdc8786c07eba39b79a51c0340ba279","tid":2026774,"uid":97080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78208e7f5f4aecc2ab6eb72838dd96114fc5f9b2","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200520/1536pix/1589957813_2be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200520%2F1536pix%2F1589957813_2be2.jpg&h=c16cf979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n95年，當年只有6歲的她跟甄子丹在電視劇《精武門》有對手戲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"甄子丹都幾長"},{"pid":"be6a9e37ccf1ce05e1cd1c84fc62f7486dff35fe","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"與Sammi有交流<br />\n<br />\n不再是幕前人，敢作敢為的戴夢夢，一直沒有為自己所做辨護，亦甘於跟再復合的Ricky低調拍拖。不過，她曾經在社交平台帖文《我們都是這樣長大的》歌詞，更獲鄭秀文親自回覆，當時正值「安心事件」過後，Sammi也有感情困擾。所以說，女人可以為愛情付出幾多，都是不能預計。"},{"pid":"d15f21b435639968d61e857573779eb3d4ecc4c6","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200520/1536pix/1589957833_2e29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200520%2F1536pix%2F1589957833_2e29.jpg&h=89871644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在ig獲鄭秀文留言後，兩人在其後上演的舞台劇再遇上。"},{"pid":"8abc16a4af95f3f0443f1d4848aba9d9e4323bfa","tid":2026774,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"詠春 葉問<br />\n太極 Ricky"},{"pid":"d1479f18001e31e44f6dfb684426f54195b9e57a","tid":2026774,"uid":182787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8abc16a4af95f3f0443f1d4848aba9d9e4323bfa","tid":2026774,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"詠春 葉問<br />\n太極 Ricky"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"FTLK?"},{"pid":"96c0a79acf53fb6e75a8c66ab731405005ae491e","tid":2026774,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8abc16a4af95f3f0443f1d4848aba9d9e4323bfa","tid":2026774,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"詠春 葉問<br />\n太極 Ricky"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"關注 迖哥"},{"pid":"ec4cd57b2d326257b10396e5a0d91fab27128e0b","tid":2026774,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"全靠你教我推車 使我壯闊一些"},{"pid":"d2310a05c06f70b0da5283a2cde2f27916760ca6","tid":2026774,"uid":322388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">    <span style=\"color: red;\">現年35歲的戴夢夢？</span></span><br />\n       <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">95年，當年只有6歲?</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0d9d3986930043e7542b84b95d5c4a6d5b4630d","tid":2026774,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2310a05c06f70b0da5283a2cde2f27916760ca6","tid":2026774,"uid":322388,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">    <span style=\"color: red;\">現年35歲的戴夢夢？</span></span><br />\n       <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">95年，當年只有6歲?</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"一定係計錯 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/12/133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif&h=25438751&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}